Podstrana, Splitsko-dalmatinska županija, Croatia

Villa is located in Podstrana, 10 km from Split. It is a perfect place for a family vacation. It is surrounded by a beautiful garden with a swimming pool and a barbecue. The villa has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a living room and a kitchen. It is fully equipped with all the necessary appliances. The villa is located 1 km from the beach and 1 km from the center of Podstrana. The nearest airport is Split Airport, 20 km from the property.
